item.title: Mopars iron miner banker is all crapped up
item.dc:creator: @KyleGut3 KyleGut3
item.description:
@KyleGut3 wrote:

macro, im going to give you some advice:

  1. if you double post a thread, people will not respond well, regardless of what you need or what your are offering.
  2. if you try to fix the problem yourself, people will respect you a lot more and be more willing to help.
  3. the majority of older scripts that you use will not work properly unless remade, if you want a well working script look in the SRL section or any script on the forums that implies dynamic coloring, they are compatable (mostly) with the update.
  4. if your only posts are requesting for help on other people’s scripts, you are labeled as a “leech” until you contribute to the community, though this forum is not anti-leech, and we aim to help anyone to be able to learn scripting etc., many members do not adhere to this policy and flame “teh l33chz0rs”.
  5. though your name may not have been intentional, it implies you are only here to steal mining scripts, maybe not your fault, but thats the vibe it gives some of the elder members here

oh and I found a copy of a SRL-ized version of mopar’s iron miner banker by Dankness in the pastebin, but I won’t post it here because it is not my work nor do I have permission to post it.

Work your way around the forum and become more aquainted with us, and hopefully you may one day come out with your own scripts.
